OL,3,CLondon's congestion charge to rise -
OL,4,Cwhat could you be paying?
OL,6,FTransport for London has launched a
OL,7,Fpublic consultation on the new
OL,8,Fcharges, which could come into effect
OL,9,Fin January.
OL,11,FThe 100% discount for EVs will be
OL,12,Freplaced by a reduced charge of #13.50
OL,13,Ffor cars and #9.00 for vans and
OL,14,Florries.
OL,16,FThe electric car discount will be cut
OL,17,Fagain in March 2030 to 12.5% which
OL,18,Fmeans drivers will pay at least #15.75.
