OL,6,FHe added: "At the same time we must
OL,7,Fsupport Londoners and businesses to
OL,8,Fuse greener and more sustainable
OL,9,Ftravel. That's why I'm pleased we're
OL,10,Fproposing that substantial incentives
OL,11,Fremain in place for Londoners who
OL,12,Fswitch to cleaner vehicles."
OL,14,FKeith Prince, from City Hall
OL,15,FConservatives, said: "These proposed
OL,16,Fchanges are going to break the backs
OL,17,Fof Londoners who have to travel via
OL,18,Froad - either for work, because of
OL,19,Fdisability, or other reasons - by
OL,20,Fslowly ramping up the cost.
