OL,6,F"After ULEZ, 20mph zones, and LTNs,
OL,7,FLabour cannot stop themselves
OL,8,Fhammering our black cabs and other
OL,9,Fdrivers in this city."
OL,11,FMichael Lloyd, from The Federation of
OL,12,FSmall Businesses, said "Many
OL,13,Fbusinesses, particularly in sectors
OL,14,Fwhere margins are so tight, will not
OL,15,Fable to absorb these extra costs.
OL,17,F"Businesses will look to charge
OL,18,Fcustomers in the charging zone a
OL,19,Fpremium for their business services
OL,20,Fwhich will heighten inflationary
OL,21,Fpressures further."
